    {
        "id":"test_guy2_yes",
        "message":"I hear some kid wiped out all the undead. The castle was heavily damaged by then, though.\n\nYou know, with a bit of funding, I think we could have that place patched up as good as new.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"How much would the repairs cost?",
                "nextPhraseID":"test_guy3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"test_guy3",
        "message":"Let me think. If we factor in the current market rate of cobblestone...yes, and then a generous supply of industrial-strength solvents for those stubborn bloodstains...labor costs should be low, there's a surplus of burly guards around here...hm, probably need to take out some liability insurance, in case there are workers' comp claims...and of course, we'll need some extra for taxes and bribery, or else Geomyr's lackeys will have the construction site shut down for dubious safety inspections...carry the one...and then budget a 30% buffer to account for planning fallacies...\n\nI'm thinking it'll take about 149,995 gold.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I happen to have that much on me right now. Here, take it.",
                "nextPhraseID":"test_guy4",
                "requires":[
                    {
                        "requireType":"inventoryRemove",
                        "requireID":"gold",
                        "value":149995
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text":"Err...sure, good luck with that.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            },
            {
                "text":"That seems like an oddly precise amount.",
                "nextPhraseID":"test_guy3_tangent"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"test_guy4",
        "message":"Wha...are you serious? How does a kid like you build up a stash like that? And how can you possibly be carrying that much? It'd weigh a ton! And...oh, hang it, what am I saying? Money talks, I listen.\n\nThank you! Castle repairs are done now. I'm a pretty fast worker when the price is right, you know.",
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"castle_repair",
                "value":1
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"test_guy3_tangent",
        "message":"Don't overthink it, kid. My father always told me never to quote a nice, round number. It makes people think you're just making things up.",
