    {
        "id":"berbane2_30",
        "message":"Now, down to business. Your first official act as my Junior Ambassador will help revitalise the local economy of Stoutford. Complete this task, and you will be hailed as a true Hero of Stoutford. And who knows? You may even rise through the ranks and find yourself with a promotion!",
