    {
        "id":"berbane2_40",
        "message":"In recent days, Stoutford has fallen on hard times. Monsters, undead, and disasters have crippled the local infrastructure. The local tavern carries only a meager selection of unappetizing provisions. This presents a unique opportunity for us. You will travel across the land and bring samples of various drinks to me. There's Blackwater brew...Remgard rum...Brimhaven brew...oh, and the wine of Castle Guynmart is delightful, I hear! Five bottles of each should suffice.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"I understand.",
                "nextPhraseID":"berbane2_50"
            },
            {
                "text":"Is this for Stoutford's economy or for your private collection?",
                "nextPhraseID":"berbane2_40b"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"bourbon_ambassador_1",
                "value":2
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"berbane2_50",
        "message":"There may be other brews out there, as well. If you find any, feel free to bring them here. The more effort you apply in this search, the better the results will be for Stoutford, I'm sure!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Sure.",
                "nextPhraseID":"berbane2_60"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"bourbon_ambassador_1",
                "value":4
